  "title": "Project Photographer (Preschool)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Scope of Work:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Take class group photos</p></li><li><p>Take individual child portraits</p></li><li><p>Work comfortably and patiently with young children in a preschool environment</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Experience photographing children (early childhood experience preferred)</p></li><li><p>Own professional camera equipment</p></li><li><p>Able to engage children naturally and capture candid, warm expressions</p></li><li><p>Reliable, punctual, and child-friendly</p></li><li><p>Able to deliver edited photos within an agreed timeline</p></li></ul><p><strong>Session Details:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Conducted during school hours</p></li><li><p>Monthly Payment</p></li></ul><p></p>",
